ygData.messageBody:
Well, Lindell said to search beneath the waves, so maybe there is a secret
cave under some water somewhere. Maybe it might even be in one of the
oceans. I'm planning on borrowing a fish bone earring from one of my guild
members (the fish bone earring gives unlimited enduring breath) and I'll
check out the oceans for a bit, heck, if I don't find any tinkering stuff,
it will be fun, and I could find something else too.

>OK guys I may just be shooting air but I thought about what he had said and
>he didnt say that it was actually under WATER. What about the catacombes
>under freeport i get lost in there a lot and there are a lot of npc's down
>there... any thoughts?
